SELECT missed_deadline_reason
FROM jobs
WHERE missed_time > 0;

SELECT SUM(j.energy_usage) AS total_energy_usage
FROM jobs j
WHERE j.user_id = 1;

external_knowledge:
- Regular users refer to those with the role 'user'.;
- Best effort urgency corresponds to the urgency level named 'BESTEFFORT'.;
- Average completion time is calculated as the difference between job completion time and start time.;

